#dashboard
  nav.fixed.top.wide.flex.align-center.justify-space-between.padding-x-small.shadow(style="min-height: 5rem")
    //- Left
    div.flex
      //- Hamburger Menu
      .menu.hide-large.center-child
        a.padding.inline-block(href="#" @click="EventBus.$emit('toggle', 'home-sidebar')")
          fa(icon="bars")
      //- Back to Home button
      .menu.show-large.center-child
        router-link.padding.inline-block(to="/")
          fa(icon="arrow-left").margin-right
          span Back to Home
      div.center-child
        span.padding
          strong My Dashboard
    //- Right
    div.center-child
      notification-button
      account-button

  //- Sidebar-Main Container
  div.flex.high(style="padding-top: 5rem")
    
    //- Sidebar
    aside.shadow.show-large.padding(style="min-width: 15rem")
      ul.remove-list-style
        li
          router-link(to="/dashboard/bookings" :class="{'active': $route.path=='/dashboard'||$route.path=='/dashboard/bookings'}").padding.inline-block.wide
            fa(icon="book" fixed-width).margin-right
            span Bookings
        li
          router-link(to="/dashboard/orders" :class="{'active': $route.path=='/dashboard/orders'}").padding.inline-block.wide
            fa(icon="shopping-cart" fixed-width).margin-right
            span Orders
    main.wide.shadow
      router-view
